claim.claim-text:
1. A method for transmitting data from a remote location to a designated device, said method comprising: 
recording subscriber information indicating the identity of a subscriber, one or more remote appliances associated the subscriber, and the characteristics of data transfer desired by the subscriber; 
collecting data at the remote location; 
transferring the data to a remote appliance; 
identifying the subscriber information corresponding to the remote appliance; and 
transmitting the data to the device based on the subscriber information.

16. An appliance for transmitting data from a remote location to a designated device, said appliance comprising: 
means for reading subscriber information indicating the identity of a subscriber associated with the remote appliance and the characteristics of data transfer desired by the subscriber; 
means for identifying a data collection device at the remote location; 
means for receiving data from the data collection device; and 
means for transmitting the data to the device based on the subscriber information.
